mitelBCM.name: mitelBCM

revisions.description: Added new BCM chip to the enumeration. Also updated copyright.
Applied stronger lint and made corrections. Also updated copyright.
Integrated in change requests and added mitelBCMChipCount.

mitelBCM.contactinfo: Standards Group, Postal: MITEL Networks Corporation 350 Legget Drive, PO Box 13089 Kanata, Ontario Canada K2K 2W7 Tel: +1 613 592 2122 Fax: +1 613 592 4784 E-mail: std@mitel.com
mitelBCM.description: The MITEL Broadcom Switch MIB module. This MIB module is defined to specifically provide additional statistical information for the Broadcom Switch subsystem.

mitelBCMPortTable.name: mitelBCMPortTable
mitelBCMPortTable.description: Table defining statistical information about each port of a Broadcom Switch sub-system.

mitelBCMPortTableEntry.name: mitelBCMPortTableEntry
mitelBCMPortTableEntry.description: A row defining a single BCM Port table entry.

mitelBCMPortIndex.name: mitelBCMPortIndex
mitelBCMPortIndex.description: The interface identifier for this switch port. Usually corresponds to ifIndex in the ifTable.

mitelBCMPortRxSAChanges.name: mitelBCMPortRxSAChanges
mitelBCMPortRxSAChanges.description: The number of times the source address (SA) of good received packets has changed. A count greater than one generally indicates the port is connected to a repeater based network.

mitelBCMPortRxLastSA.name: mitelBCMPortRxLastSA
mitelBCMPortRxLastSA.description: The last received source address on this port.

mitelBCMChipCount.name: mitelBCMChipCount
mitelBCMChipCount.description: The number of BCM ethernet chips in the system.

mitelBCMChipTable.name: mitelBCMChipTable
mitelBCMChipTable.description: Table defining characteristic information about each Broadcom Switch chip in the system.

mitelBCMChipTableEntry.name: mitelBCMChipTableEntry
mitelBCMChipTableEntry.description: A row defining a single Broadcom (BCM) Chip table entry.

mitelBCMChipIndex.name: mitelBCMChipIndex
mitelBCMChipIndex.description: The identifier for this switch chip.

mitelBCMChipBIST.name: mitelBCMChipBIST
mitelBCMChipBIST.description: The status of the BCM ethernet chip built-in-self-test (BIST). BCRAM(0) bit 2^0 - Buffer control RAM (only in BCM5380M) IPDBM(1) bit 2^1 - Internal packet data buffer memory MRAM(2) bit 2^2 - MIB RAM (only in BCM5380M) GMRAM(3) bit 2^3 - Gigabit MIB RAM (only in BCM5380M) If the bit is set, then that sub-system has failed.

mitelBCMChipRev.name: mitelBCMChipRev
mitelBCMChipRev.description: The BCM ethernet chip revision ID.

mitelBCMSwitchCompliance.name: mitelBCMSwitchCompliance
mitelBCMSwitchCompliance.description: The compliance statement for mitel nodes that include a BCM switch sub-system.

mitelBCMPortGroup.name: mitelBCMPortGroup
mitelBCMPortGroup.description: A collection of objects that provide statistical infrormation about BCM switch ports.

mitelBCMChipGroup.name: mitelBCMChipGroup
mitelBCMChipGroup.description: A collection of objects that provide infrormation about BCM switch Chips.
